{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b1af18218","title":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5ebf73d859","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"3b1af18218"}],"tags":[{"id":"2bffb53b5b","name":"对外关系和政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e22203f556","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"90680ba05d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫作发展中的国家。你不要看我国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，Isay（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"53416508fa","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化——包括语言一—的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"5dd26bd0db","type":"paragraph","text":"1973年6月22日，毛泽东会见马里共和国总理特拉奥雷。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"}],"page":{"id":"247bf9731a","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","start":413,"end":413}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9b6de51e39","type":"paragraph","text":"（外交部绝密文件，文特43）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"9c6ccef2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化──包括语言──的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"df357a47ab","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"ebc28c048c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫做发展中的国家。你不要看中国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，I SAY（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218"}],"page":{"id":"61c485c2c7","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}